| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2778 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 193ef50f-98ed-54c3-8685-faa7e149e8ac"
